  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka man scho Leetu ta bij grohſiht/ to irr taws Kalps Jo- abs darrijs. Bet mans Kungs irr gudrs pehz tahs Gudribas weena Deeva Engeta/ ka wiꞥſch wiſtu warr ſinnaht/ kas wirs Semmes noteek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Rehninsch fazzija us Joabu: Rangi jelle/ es eſmu ſcho Leetu padarrijs. Eij tad/ un atwedd to Puist Absalonn at- pakkak.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad mettehs Joabs us fawu Waign pee Semmes/ un peehudſe/ un pateize tam Rehni- nam/ un Joabs fazzija: Scho- deen irr taws Kalps noimannijs/ ka es Schehlaſtibu eſmu atraddis preekſch ta Kunga manna Reh- nina/ tapehz ka tas Rehninsch to Wahrdn fawa Kalpa padarrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta zehlehs Joabs/ un gabje uhs Gesuru/ un wedde Ab- salomu uhs Jeruſalemi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Rehninsch fazzija: Lai wiꞥſch fawa Namna eet/ un preekſch mannahm Azzim ne nahk. Tad gabje Absaloms fa- wa Namna/ un ne redſeja ta Rehnixa Waign.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu bija ne kahds Wihrs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiꞥſch fawn Gal- wn arzirpe/ (tas noticke tik ue itgaddus/ ka wiꞥſch to nozirpe/ tapehz ka tee Matti winuain wiſſai greuhti bija/ tad nozirpe wiꞥſch tohs/) tad wilke winna Galwas Matti diwisints Sih- ketus/ pehz ta Rehnixa Swarra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Absalomain kuna arridsan trihs Dehli dsimmuschi/ un weena Meita Tahmara Wahrida/ ta bija weena kobtt skaista Seewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta politke Absaloms Je- rusalemē diwt Gaddus/ unne redſeja ta Rehnixa Watgu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz fuhtija Absaloms pee Joabu/ ka wiꞥſch to pee ta Rehnixa tuhtitu/ bet tas negrib- beja pee ta nabkt. Tad fuhtija wiꞥſch wehl ohtru Reisi/ un tas wehl ne gribbeja nahkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch us fa- weem Kalpeem: Redsi/ Joaba Tihrumis irr pee manna klahtu/ un winnam irr Meechi us to/ eita/ un eededſinajeet to ar Ug- guni. Tad eededſinaja Absalo- ma Kalpi to Tihrumu ar Ugguni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Joabs/ un nahze Absaloma Namna/ un fazzija us to: Rapehz irr tawi Kalpi mannu Tihrumu ar Uggu- ni eededſinajſchi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Absaloms fazzija us Joabu: Rangi/ es eſmu pee tew\n"
    }
  ],
